  "body": "This a pretty weird bug. All 4 times, the same random numbers are generated. While probably not imminently critical, an enterprising scammer could take advantage of this\n\n![screen shot 2016-02-06 at 8 24 04 pm](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1577353/12870382/df08d1fa-cd0f-11e5-9684-53292c77e67b.png)\n\nHere's the contents of randomtest.js\n\n```\nfor(var i = 0; i<5; i++){\n    console.log(Math.random())\n}\nprocess.exit()\n```\n",
